headline: 82% of Americans Use AI for Housing Market Information, Realtor.com® Survey Finds
summary: The majority of Americans are embracing new tools to navigate the housing market, with 82% using AI for real estate insights, according to a new survey from Realtor.com®. Yet despite these shifts, consumers say real estate agents remain the most trusted and accurate source of information.

headline: Search It, How You Say It: Realtor.com® Launches New AI-Powered Search
summary: Nearly two- thirds of current and potential home searchers are frustrated about not being able to search for a home based on what they care about. Today, Realtor.com® is changing that with the launch of its new AI-powered search experience, which is designed to let people find homes the way they actually talk and type.
